    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay, so if i just use the drops and some warm compresses, it should be fine for a few days right? i'm also thinking of taking some ibuprofen to help with the pain since it's stinging a bit. as long as the redness doesn't get way worse, i don't really see a reason to go to the doctor yet, do you?",
